name: Kra Bong Tong
description:
Parodia leninghausii cactus, I call it Kra Bong Tong . I've grown from a small tree until now, almost 20 years ago, just now blooming. It took a very long time to be patient.
Made me think If you wait patiently with hope No matter how long it takes In the end, there is always success.
My Kra Bong Tong  has not only produced one flower, and there are two.
